sentences: Joshua Donald Fauver (December 4, 1978 – November 2, 2018) was an American musician.
He served as the longtime bassist for the Atlanta, Georgia band Deerhunter from 2004 to 2012.
Fauver replaced the original Deerhunter bassist Justin Bosworth in 2004.

Fauver played on their debut self-titled album (2004), Cryptograms (2007), the Fluorescent Grey EP (2007), Weird Era and Microcastle (2008), Rainwater Cassette Exchange EP (2009), and Halcyon Digest (2010).
